::DevilDuer/Zardus/Lavacons::

DevilDuer surfaced above the water, squeezing inbetween the two feet 
that were between the edge of the Alliance island and the shields. He 
climbs ashore, looking up at Zardus, who was standing not too far 
away.

"Hey, boss!" he says, getting up and walking over to Zardus, "I got a 
new recruit for ya!"

Zardus turns from looking at the destroyed shore, looking at 
DevilDuer. The battle was good as won anyways.

"Hmm? Excellent. Good work. Where's the new bot?"

DevilDuer turns around, waiting for Bigfish to get here.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Griplash surfaces above the water, swimming toward the steaming 
rubble that used to be a shore.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
To missiles exploded against Recklessa's side, sending her spinning 
off sideways and dropping Astral into the water. 
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
"Understood," Slayer says and turns, flying at full speed toward 
Iguanus' signal.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Fenox flies over the shots, one of them hitting her in the leg and 
nearly disabling it. She growls, firing her rifle down at Prebon.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Starlight lands on the ground, pulling out her charge launcher and 
firing at Prebon.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Havoc flies out of the safety of the shields of the Alliance base, 
pursuing Slayer and firing rapidly at the bot.
